    "description": "In the past, the insatiable greed of jinns and mythical creatures led to the splitting of the crystal into six parts, dispersing them to all corners of the world.<br><br>Manipulation, provocation, and incitement are tactics consistently employed by jinns to reclaim the entirety of the crystal's power.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/8586a79b040ad90785e3d7e9ef268bce.poster.avif?t=1727497790\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/8586a79b040ad90785e3d7e9ef268bce.webm?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/8586a79b040ad90785e3d7e9ef268bce.mp4?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In the medieval era, a child chosen by the gods possesses a unique talent. Utilize these abilities to rescue the crystal from malevolence and avert the world's impending destruction.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/2ac0603b315b2b3d20d8cff45f91b17f.avif?t=1727497790\" width=620 height=92 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/bb7ab947d696bdee5e43f974a43ccbe2.poster.avif?t=1727497790\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/bb7ab947d696bdee5e43f974a43ccbe2.webm?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/bb7ab947d696bdee5e43f974a43ccbe2.mp4?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each character possesses varying strengths, exhibiting unique personalities and fighting styles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/dae8035468a86bda286409da262adc68.avif?t=1727497790\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br>Each region harbors formidable heroes, each with distinct abilities and summoning capabilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/40dc8171251177e5ab02856cd83affd5.avif?t=1727497790\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br>A supernatural protective figure is possessed by heroes in various regions, each having different powers and origins according to their owners.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/75d66dac2937baa86e4e9cdf939c3cdb.poster.avif?t=1727497790\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/75d66dac2937baa86e4e9cdf939c3cdb.webm?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/75d66dac2937baa86e4e9cdf939c3cdb.mp4?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Experience the excitement of turn-based combat, leveraging the unique skills of each hero. Strategize by combining their abilities for optimal effectiveness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/4cc49670a860f11f8159e9c68ead7148.poster.avif?t=1727497790\" width=640 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/4cc49670a860f11f8159e9c68ead7148.webm?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/4cc49670a860f11f8159e9c68ead7148.mp4?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enhance the bond between your hero and their summons, experiencing newfound powers as they grow stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/b411284bd1b2043b55cec9e491a8e4ae.avif?t=1727497790\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br>Immerse yourself in the fusion of Nusantara culture with Japanese nuances, creating a unique gaming experience that blends two distinct cultures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/af8784b7edffa316aecb99b3e1aaf0ae.poster.avif?t=1727497790\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/af8784b7edffa316aecb99b3e1aaf0ae.webm?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/af8784b7edffa316aecb99b3e1aaf0ae.mp4?t=1727497790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use teleportation to expedite travel and reduce the time spent moving between locations.",
